'it's worth noting that starting from Drools 7, the concept of StatefulKnowledgeSession has been replaced by the KieSession, which provides similar functionality but with improved performance and better integration capabilities.

The term "StatefulKnowledgeSession" is associated with the Drools rule engine, specifically with the earlier versions of Drools (prior to version 7). Drools is a popular open-source rule engine that allows you to define and execute business rules in various applications.
